[v1.1 -- gate loosening, evidence-collection phase]
Reason: No trade has accumulated yet. All thresholds were guesses with
no data behind them. Phase 4 exists to collect that data — restricting
entry before any trades close defeats the purpose of the calibration engine.
ALLOWED_ENTRY_QUALITIES: GOOD, MODERATE, WEAK, EXTENDED (all accepted)
CONFIDENCE_FLOOR: REMOVED (set to 0, never filters)
MIN_RR_FOR_ENTRY: REMOVED (set to 0.0, never filters)
MAX_MOVE_EXTENSION_PCT: None (no cap, unchanged)
CONFIDENCE_FLOOR and MIN_RR_FOR_ENTRY retained as variables in
financial_standards.py so live_engine.py import does not break.
Tighten only after Phase 4B produces evidence.
